{"id":"28593ef39d168933c00d63635a49470583b1a6634c0248705776169c585d447d","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:0","text":"使用聚合体积工作流渲染的 Moana Cloud 资产。OpenVDB 资产由"}
{"id":"bfc4f82c1220a189671601fe7ec6ef5f1e6c699f1677484bc0c9eb6242f3a3f5","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:1","text":"Walt Disney Animation 提供"}
{"id":"5975213b61b0c2db14643c803368d253a9f2bf6d138f6ff5b9305f703a162576","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:3","text":"CC BY-SA 3.0"}
{"id":"5c0c2d079d17ffb0561026bae14d284518eb3393a1ee22820d7a65e37c108a64","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:4","text":"许可证。"}
{"id":"c42659233ea7238ffee7eb47622b88127b5ed7ec8accec711f55390a80c4defa","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:5","text":"使用聚合体积工作流渲染云时，可以调整若干关键设置来控制云的外观。本页所有图像都使用在 RfM 中搭建的场景渲染。有关场景设置的说明，请参阅"}
{"id":"6ffdc2d20e61ead5b3da88ffca4d10a25d6911ed229db06e2bf5e77144e7718b","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:6","text":"场景设置"}
{"id":"6ffdc2d20e61ead5b3da88ffca4d10a25d6911ed229db06e2bf5e77144e7718b","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:117","text":"场景设置"}
{"id":"1e54a9f638505a5f5067dfaf2421931c270a61bf21fecf1597c263b883a3298a","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:7","text":"一节。"}
{"id":"0b3c28ede68c89c59246e77f9562f5d7d774e1664ab38844d1348f0c66429bcc","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:8","text":"体积设置"}
{"id":"bd7da363642d43b65c02bf7d32a0b434b4a696817d80d50751febb2be677384d","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:9","text":"Max Path Length"}
{"id":"74f1bf32df8e35cc43b27b147ede6cb5245d004625b0af7e8c233b6e944dea90","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:10","text":"渲染云时，最大路径长度是极其重要的控制项。要得到类似云的外观，需要相对较高的最大路径长度。下方图像分别使用最大路径长度 0、16 和 64 渲染。"}
{"id":"7ae63a9a6ea0bcef9cbca9a9abff3f21935e817b13a2f03ed9dd3da8a361de37","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:11","text":"在更高路径长度下变化会更细微，但若要让云的阴影区域出现明显的光线渗透，就需要非常高的最大路径长度。"}
{"id":"4426e0e91c4746af10130ef891955a5ca6168a844c58b8c4140e301076afa43e","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:12","text":"路径长度为 64（左）和 256（右）时的云场景渲染结果。"}
{"id":"90b2d7813288e186d504ff9f7e725de3629d983d0051bc76e78708741c710d43","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:13","text":"提高最大路径长度也会增加渲染时间，因此应尽量保持较低。Volume Scattering Approximation（见下文）可以用低得多的成本模拟高路径长度的效果。"}
{"id":"3d3bfc99cb73a63c9b81320642751d7fd9e5edec195711288b5355e874d86b26","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:154","text":"Volume Scattering Approximation"}
{"id":"5911af17ef4ddf4467656f3a64b181b7c00c958eb89970dd187a7d6a3190fe77","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:15","text":"Volume Scattering Approximation 设置是一组用于模拟体积内多重散射效果的设置。正确设置时，Volume Scattering Approximation 可以产生类似非常高路径长度的外观，同时不会增加渲染时间。Volume Scattering Approximation 有三个控制项："}
{"id":"4e125a3ef68a00b029459c9aa8aa94aa07e74cc54188ffef7f60f38f016e61ca","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:156","text":"Gain"}
{"id":"2574b5ca76b0782c9d1c8d5558d32fa74df5b6e0aeb30ea4b7cd0ab0fb0be9de","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:158","text":"Bleed"}
{"id":"126e55b257ac9c816d23a1310f8b3bfe8dde590622adda0cbb3456e2c59f2ab9","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:160","text":"Contribution"}
{"id":"2e98e2dcf2060d05562901f347cbe38620b2c45ec023fea531015320b6b66eb4","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:20","text":"。每个设置的效果见下文。虽然"}
{"id":"619332d197056053fb100a85c26ccdf41ab59a6109c7af50c0b5875cad01ada6","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:24","text":"都是颜色，但下文用一个单一数值指代它们，该数值会同时用于红、绿、蓝三个通道。"}
{"id":"49159df56606fcddb52e49ab5be7d35aec4537d98115a7cbcad4471fb28a6e71","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:28","text":"参数用于在灯光上启用或禁用 Volume Scattering Approximation。应将它设为 1，并调整"}
{"id":"f25ca69db06cdc86d008373e99a74060c93805e074fd7c606586bd8a70a4c72b","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:32","text":"设置以获得所需效果。将"}
{"id":"90c790934e7a501abb01d716a318174c0c62f4b956eea7920607c07f9bfbf376","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:34","text":"设置为 [0,1] 范围之外的值可能产生不正确的结果。"}
{"id":"d3b4d228c66cad5cad579ff8348465638980f1614ce2da373634f1a345d7134f","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:35","text":"云场景渲染结果，其中"}
{"id":"d3b4d228c66cad5cad579ff8348465638980f1614ce2da373634f1a345d7134f","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:68","text":"云场景渲染结果，其中"}
{"id":"f62c9dc5adc5309a3ca03ac81802855c24020a628a6cd264822fa41e6be00d2b","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:37","text":"设为 0（左）和 1（右），并使用默认的"}
{"id":"818cd8d91aea3a1689455f009f49e87fe7fa647fa2c4b9f09072dd1c33d52ca5","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:42","text":"将"}
{"id":"d326e838ab6960bab843b682c1f1a5f8b2950bc1e922b94c4b158c004ed6452b","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:44","text":"设置为 [0,1] 范围之外的值可能无法产生视觉上正确的图像"}
{"id":"c4321efbbae20101d01badc020b067c0569feb63cde972d9ab92710a51642c70","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:48","text":"参数控制有多少光线会渗透穿过体积。更高的"}
{"id":"3e14423b0fb650768816e8cb0080f3f67000e748bc8387e7b99057d2ef2f50f5","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:50","text":"值会允许更多光线穿过体积，并照亮原本处于阴影中的区域。因此，"}
{"id":"f7a5b303d5d9260d19d62775fcb40e39857f11f7e0905d7a19b48094464e280a","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:52","text":"的效果在体积的阴影区域最明显，但它也会带来轻微的整体增亮效果。可以使用渗透（Bleed）参数来补偿较低 Max Path Length 导致的整体亮度损失。"}
{"id":"d3b4d228c66cad5cad579ff8348465638980f1614ce2da373634f1a345d7134f","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:53","text":"云场景渲染结果，其中"}
{"id":"984512b41ced1b8c9cd915d0f23920dda944f87619062af4d2848428871d91b0","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:55","text":"设为 0.1（左）和 0.9（右），并使用默认的"}
{"id":"1df0e6e33e0b7c61e5ab2e002d52d10da3a34021c57fe0719c27c79275e2e28a","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:61","text":"参数控制来自"}
{"id":"83616ca343af7adf18d64cb83fcccc92aec50cfe3cf6cade61bff50fcb260791","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:63","text":"参数的光线渗透会在多大程度上贡献到体积亮度。提高"}
{"id":"a529d66edaadfb650229028a8ae2bfeb6cec343bc6274a4b52e76ac64f9ccdd8","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:65","text":"通常会提高云的整体亮度，但对边缘的增亮略少。可以使用"}
{"id":"fe3c02065ddf9ba8ffd2ed5ad203e3fa848012fc7de2fb939d5dd6749e8ef035","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:67","text":"来帮助呈现体积边缘的细节。"}
{"id":"1c0ba31424bb634d1d23feb03ba4c8165d58aa22eebbe23caf9c511cc8167e17","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:70","text":"设为 0.25（左）和 0.75（右），并使用默认的"}
{"id":"1c0601250db503ca50a6004ea3a9555509b3b9a39e6f186c10e57b29def598b9","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:71","text":"Bleed。"}
{"id":"0805e81453776b630b4fd7fe067075b5ca1fb5b0e642f0bb76366c3ea87e8f94","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:72","text":"Volume Scattering Approximation 调参建议"}
{"id":"cf94e7fb2e5e5e4106a65d009a314a63e5fcc6749abf7aecbfbc32c61684ee86","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:73","text":"要为"}
{"id":"7dc2f38fcdab9495e81ad20bbfc4067009ab49f7d67ab29bec41acf1974308c8","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:77","text":"找到合适的值可能并不容易，因为二者相互依赖很强。可以尝试的流程是先将"}
{"id":"36cf996848f0092e910c10599a5ebc4d600cdd6569dcc8f563e553be92603e25","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:79","text":"设为 1，然后交替小幅提高"}
{"id":"e3b3fb2f9760752ea4eeedfc46dd4eae7354c1fc02939d9dcb057ca7c02c8171","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:81","text":"并降低"}
{"id":"aa4cef37f4985df017b9964e28f51d06277a98b25a56567ea08e895e2e5df5bb","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:83","text":"，直到阴影区域的亮度达到正确平衡。"}
{"id":"18d9a854238ae67cd4911c02ff2a7c12bb7dbfe682f5b64db5b55bed029eeeaa","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:85","text":"会产生更强的增亮效果，因此调整步幅应小于"}
{"id":"9988b9845cc8a169b6bd7be97ff4b7bafb4c75ccddd1ff9617c9165b002d2b83","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:88","text":"当数值较高时，"}
{"id":"35178347681e9adf9244e2e1838d3361855a243ff82c0d954eea234bf247b3c9","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:90","text":"参数会变得非常敏感，因此在接近 1 时应以小增量（0.05 或更小）调整。"}
{"id":"77a283d69258c2ae985dc2343725d0af253da0fc1d87626966f7cefe4a3c7469","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:91","text":"密度"}
{"id":"3b8634bf3f07b0d4b7949e85fd5972fbde5062dbbac73b24186163374bfe2258","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:92","text":"云的密度会显著影响它的外观。密度的主要控制项是体积上的"}
{"id":"be69b95dc76c36a8a97c294b29e25cbd972b97f1cb70531c85518a1577de9d93","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:99","text":"Density Scale"}
{"id":"1952a730c5bd55d2625f9307ff0a33d4d660f9db7b59dca208b91a1711f42bce","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:94","text":"设置，它会缩放输入 OpenVDB 文件中的密度。较低的"}
{"id":"4b01f1d9603d10e5a0c38b8d687187718f38e6f421046cf0e21b1d70dd588312","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:96","text":"值会产生更轻盈、更少细节且光线渗透更多的外观，而较高的"}
{"id":"e4bfaca2f7c6b7240725ce9f862343a217bea67ca699a08416674a81bcf1086a","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:98","text":"值会产生更厚重、更有细节，甚至接近实体的外观。下方图像使用"}
{"id":"1ea4ebef4bfa1136b1c68024599a638fb0cdb4da28a4e6853c01e3f683af79ca","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:100","text":" 的取值分别为 0.2、1.0 和 5.0。"}
{"id":"8d92c2498f5ca083b4554452796bb60e0c21fed9667a057002c36465571d949d","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:101","text":"Anisotropy"}
{"id":"1d1887f9ae7fed329b6336bbc0a48d8ea77ae18a8b300a11a2f5dbc2fb7cf3f3","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:102","text":"调整 PxrVolume 中的各向异性设置，对于获得真实的云渲染同样关键。需要注意三个各向异性设置：Primary Anisotropy、Secondary Anisotropy 和 Lobe Blend Factor。Primary Anisotropy 与 Secondary Anisotropy 设置控制两个各向异性波瓣，它们可以是前向散射（设为 +1）或后向散射（设为 -1）。Lobe Blend 控制两个波瓣的相对贡献，其中 0 表示只使用 Primary 波瓣，1 表示只使用 Secondary 波瓣。将 Primary 波瓣设为前向散射会压平云中某些区域的细节，但也会让面向光源的云体部分变暗。"}
{"id":"e04cf951b16f850139c9c27ca7ab64d488ea86b330777493faeb81e4d2c485bd","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:103","text":"云场景渲染结果，左侧未使用各向异性，右侧使用前向散射 Primary 波瓣，其中"}
{"id":"79e06d7f2451e2b60e308f9d4d57c4e7c8f1284376a5bd1cf286b0ff07c1a46a","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:110","text":"Primary Anisotropy"}
{"id":"6cbf88803215ea23e50f07faabe4cb28c4beee1a7df6a4c21db0022b921902fc","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:105","text":"设为 0.8，且"}
{"id":"ee6cfb23a65ea3810217bda90b013cb26c870677d482023ac4263552d5e3d31e","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:114","text":"Blend"}
{"id":"b54922fe5ab9656f9d9548c5174976918b809665adc4e0fc8465ac7064541ea1","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:107","text":"设为 0。"}
{"id":"ae3c49d0072900483aa6600131397669623290599d8b80789fd15fd51fca4ab4","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:108","text":"添加后向散射 Secondary 波瓣，可以恢复前向散射渲染中丢失的大部分细节，同时仍保留面向光源区域中的部分细节。"}
{"id":"b90addd3322b49eddec18440a344ffe8d8bdef6850bb44fd6eb46b30d09ccfc3","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:109","text":"云场景渲染结果，左侧未使用各向异性，右侧使用前向散射 Primary 波瓣和后向散射 Secondary 波瓣，其中"}
{"id":"f67894e3bfecb38ba227bd319cc4d274e44193e5469a089724065d2c328f58ca","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:111","text":"设为 0.8，"}
{"id":"c56e4107af6cd77c5c3c78d7604b3415ae9d0d4ee03f6f3497fb8c676cda0b5a","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:112","text":"Secondary Anisotropy 设为 -0.2"}
{"id":"6201111b83a0cb5b0922cb37cc442b9a40e24e3b1ce100a4bb204f4c63fd2ac0","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:113","text":"且"}
{"id":"1adc0f9185501fe959e6c292325ca1d80a68011ca07e47d4fc92cef6e36608ec","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:115","text":"设为 0.2。"}
{"id":"110b017c333044aa30230171a54c85ad7093861eaff90355e6c3db053563044f","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:116","text":"启用各向异性会给渲染引入额外噪声。各向异性数值越高，引入的噪声越多。"}
{"id":"99dc691e89fedc5a6e8f0fdc8d869e94825dfb04f30986ae089affc62639d83c","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:118","text":"本节介绍上面使用的场景是如何在 RfM 中设置的。"}
{"id":"4c4f29f1f7b7b1ea8dc17cc4fd7a9bded1210fc6423779800e92efd2a8c84ae2","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:119","text":"体积设置"}
{"id":"34dd90fd9b50af47a374639cd62d611008d4353cebc4f5f5e895d9b45e15154b","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:120","text":"首先，从 RenderMan 工具架标签页创建一个 OpenVDBVisualize 对象。"}
{"id":"afd34862d23cc8bb29377199e1c85a18a4418c612cdd2284f79101a166105160","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:121","text":"接下来，在属性编辑器的 OpenVDBRead 设置中选择要使用的 VDB 文件（Moana Cloud 的四分之一或八分之一分辨率版本很适合用于调试设置）。"}
{"id":"e0c0deefff011afdab17f14f3505c62a868537b31ca912e2843b99a0004dc390","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:122","text":"现在，你应该能在视口中看到叶节点和 tile 的线框（可能需要缩小视图才能看到整朵云）。接着，在大纲视图中选择 OpenVDBVisualize 对象，并在属性编辑器中打开 OpenVDBVisualize 设置。在这里，应旋转体积，使云的顶部朝向 +Z 方向。因此，沿 X 轴添加 90 度旋转。"}
{"id":"6ae28b19bff81edf2f04864904d7587f7c09ca8dc24bc5cd647c29361d817a9d","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:123","text":"请确保在 OpenVDBVisualizeShape 节点上启用 “Visible in Reflections”，该选项位于 Render Stats 部分。此设置在 Maya 中默认关闭；为了得到正确的光线多重散射，需要将它开启。"}
{"id":"9219e13981609e60b6b2931e015cc45d38014eca93a713b05629fdbf763143f7","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:124","text":"体积设置中最后需要做的是把该体积加入体积聚合。globalVolumeAggregate 会自动创建，因此在 OpenVDBVisualizeShape 设置中的 RenderMan > Volume Aggregate 下，将"}
{"id":"87502e491b5201b5f4f4b84e63757a7ab09fa8221d018fd4d38fd943ba3e9273","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:125","text":"Aggregate Membership"}
{"id":"29fefc8a236ce155f2c77bbd1a62013417a5e91743e40809d394b5c8c1189506","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:126","text":"设置为 “globalVolumeAggregate”。"}
{"id":"938e4e0d46f923fbaaa29399eaeb3e1893606859f9e08ead7cf0a7f252106031","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:127","text":"你可能还希望禁用叶节点和活动 tile 的可视化；该选项位于 OpenVDB Visualization Settings 下。"}
{"id":"99f89df21d0dff581411423b799902bef1efeedf77bb48e8c712478f72755743","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:128","text":"体积着色器设置"}
{"id":"31d8df0a5353692c3de32c9c3bb2faf0b16ad25f406ebe74ad1dc7e4312e7155","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:129","text":"在着色器设置中，也可以在 Anisotropy 区域调整各向异性设置。默认情况下，各向异性处于关闭状态。"}
{"id":"7a0080214f4f354d13fe35d00823223025fd920abff93a5496409131de552548","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:130","text":"灯光设置"}
{"id":"dbe50feab96cb385594e53c4874765da4289ee289491e3833fea77aa97f85482","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:131","text":"灯光设置将使用 PxrEnvDayLight。因此，灯光设置的第一步是从工具架的 RenderMan 标签页创建一个 PxrEnvDayLight。"}
{"id":"b3df29e000b06a18ca6a9ea5cce184fcaddd17bd18d9934f28dc96a018f122ec","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:132","text":"接下来，可以在属性编辑器的 PxrEnvDayLightShape 标签页中调整灯光方向，可以使用"}
{"id":"310ca503ef36f177ddbc760463fcaec1edc6eca12bfd590ad7bb244b31e59543","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:133","text":"Month"}
{"id":"8f2364e11b8be3ff008f32b3dedb54e659362429bcc9e3eb6acb6070de4ffbff","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:134","text":"Day"}
{"id":"89f6832560dec0b7f8721d1fe3ba0b5036a5d1464ce4339bb16c3e1485bfec34","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:135","text":"Year"}
{"id":"f0063b808736318d3f5038c3a6c3b6349183cc678ed93d2e7963248ae7ed7318","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:136","text":"Hour"}
{"id":"dccf31fdd01f1a2d433262a306989dac0a0fe0829029a55ae730720970838eba","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:137","text":"（这是 RfM 中的默认方法），也可以使用"}
{"id":"9c8a9579abe55bdc8a7b97031705e2738d912de38a35262863d8f47e05d3d641","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:138","text":"Direction"}
{"id":"80333f3538ee9b53e530367f172c12caf5a0882b96e15bae5b00918681490093","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:139","text":"控制项，方法是选择 Month > Use Direction。要复现本教程使用的场景，请使用方向控制项，并将方向设置为 0.8、1.0、0.6。还应将"}
{"id":"d6d397f3c91d53285b287a378cbd35bd021fa59cd21578681954cd4a281f07a5","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:140","text":"Ground Mode"}
{"id":"5d41f124154035b3fc45a02e25571fc4bf39ad4065ef51e8bc9432e323aeb7bd","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:141","text":"从 “Legacy” 改为 “Horizon Clamping”。"}
{"id":"ddd35b9f421c04dc8c455f3e946ab02543fada354704ec5d9b76d3fa95d83034","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:142","text":"其他默认值提供了不错的起点，因此现在可以先保持不变。这里也是调整 Volume Scattering Approximation 设置的位置。Volume Scattering Approximation 对渲染的影响可能很难预测，因此应等渲染完全设置好之后再调整这些设置。"}
{"id":"82e971defec02bee07dc78266c242eaf0a00426b8988dfdb2a864da6e8f8576c","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:143","text":"渲染设置"}
{"id":"c03532ea1b031a9d0a1eae52943e7aad3c3aedcb16154f2e17dffeba9b4f461e","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:144","text":"要看到渲染出的云，最后需要修改的是 Render Settings。打开 Render Settings 并选择 RenderMan 标签页。首先要在 “Aggregate Volumes” 标签页下修改"}
{"id":"068c4214f7fa7a7c3ceec977cacac06909051a18b82bc5ecc95bad5609eb1fde","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:145","text":"Volume Aggregate Name"}
{"id":"dd7468eab3be565799d86878df0626ee79f3287c8eaafbd1337634a8cf7cfa5a","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:146","text":"，输入 “globalVolumeAggregate”（这就是我们之前把云加入的体积聚合）。"}
{"id":"12c837ae71fd04e2e26144e000020fc48f96c1306f5d06a84a2c6cbb84678fbc","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:147","text":"设置体积聚合名称后，如果开始渲染（无论是在视口中，还是在外部 “it” 中），应该就能看到云，但它看起来仍然不会完全正确。要让云具有正确外观，需要调整反弹次数。首先，在 “Default Ray Depth” 下，将"}
{"id":"5c425c17a027d583a483a67f371869d2bda2ada15206103b5490b66e10c1ac76","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:148","text":"Max Specular Depth"}
{"id":"9d0ae77780b7481633efaf5833c59a92292ec12ec5787726459b6021800d959a","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:150","text":"Max Diffuse Depth"}
{"id":"42dd4cc44922a40ba7c9840a6d1ddbf8d2fb12033acfc6192977f25cd6892699","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:151","text":"都调高（如上所述），并在 “PxrPathTracer Parameters” 下将"}
{"id":"f3a6b79ecafe9f7f98671b7823c46d64507d1dae0ceb6144a5028f59348aa531","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:152","text":"Max Indirect Bounces"}
{"id":"bde16945c9f1f4d30b028d7d5327cfe767caa8eccc055f11ca9527c467a8c553","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:153","text":"设置为同一个数值。"}
{"id":"f67423ce1e373d44e2dc7c9e52b006bc337f6a94cfba3bda5376ba224ca467dc","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:155","text":"要调整 Volume Scattering Approximation 设置，请转到 PxrEnvDayLight 的设置，并通过将"}
{"id":"8c4b29349e3eed04276463fdf29809307ac1a2e62131f6ffb4ae0e4d13d0e5f9","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:157","text":"设为 1 来启用 Volume Scattering Approximation。现在，可以调整"}
{"id":"ceb8e444711e91245c97312ced22ab29601690c20ccd567df3c55fb1d56f13d8","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:161","text":"，如上所述。"}
{"id":"6d89eb7d0938564938636b4a5ee73c09e55c2e6e5aaa9e3016781bf54805e8d3","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:162","text":"渲染"}
{"id":"118a375be33956ef781012c4f2aaef937ceb6bfd9d47a909fd9206333c8bf3c6","item_id":"a2c90b4a99:163","text":"现在所有设置都已完成，可以启动渲染并查看云，结果应类似这样："}
{"id": "cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8", "item_id": "a2c90b4a99:2", "text": "。"}
{"id": "b344d80e24a3679999fa964450b34bc24d1578a35509f934c1418b0a20d21a67", "item_id": "a2c90b4a99:26", "text": "该"}
